### Task 1 : 48bb6e862e54f2a795ffc4e541caed4d

**Step 1** - Find the hash type on https://hashes.com/en/tools/hash_identifier

!image.png

Hash Type : MD5

Step 2 - store the hash in a txt file ( Crack_This in this case )

Step 3 - Use Hashcat to crack the hash, alternatively you can use John the Ripper also.

- Hash Cat

!image.png

```purescript
hashcat -m 0 -a 3 Crack_This /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt

hashcat -m 0 -a 3 Crack_This --show
```

***Plain Text : easy***

- John the Ripper

```purescript
john --format=raw-md5 --wordlist=/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt Crack_This
```

